GeneralComments:
Consult website - open during business hours, and late night when astronomy sessions run. If possible, email or phone ahead of time to confirm there aren't other heavy users of electrical equipment (food carts, music gigs, etc).
Available at no extra cost for customers while visiting Stonehenge Aotearoa for daytime tours, events, and night-time astronomy sessions. http://www.stonehenge-aotearoa.co.nz/ and info@stonehenge-aotearoa.co.nz
